<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Dentistry - Password Reset Successful</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
   <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/password-reset/reset-password-success.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="left">
      <img src="/img/dentist.jpg" alt="Dental clinic interior" />
    </div>
    
    <div class="right">
      <div class="content-box">
        <div class="brand">
          <h2>Dentistry</h2>
          <div class="subtitle">Password Reset</div>
        </div>

        <div class="success-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
        </div>

        <div class="success-message">
          <div class="success-title">Your password has been updated successfully!</div>
          You can now log in with your new password.
        </div>

        <div class="timestamp">
          Changed at: <span id="timestamp"></span>
        </div>

        <div class="info-section">
          <h4>What happens next?</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Your old password is no longer valid</li>
            <li>All active sessions have been logged out for security</li>
            <li>A confirmation email has been sent to your email address</li>
            <li>You can now log in using your new password</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="security-info">
          <strong>Security Note:</strong>
          For your security, if you didn't make this change, please contact our support team immediately. We recommend using strong, unique passwords and enabling two-factor authentication where available.
        </div>

        <div class="action-buttons">
          <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary" id="loginBtn">
            <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> Go to Login
          </a>
          
          <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary">
            <i class="fas fa-home"></i> Go to Home
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="countdown" id="countdown">
          You will be automatically redirected to login page in <span id="timer">10</span> seconds...
        </div>

        <div class="footer-info">
          <p><strong>Need Help?</strong></p>
          <p>If you're having trouble accessing your account or have any security concerns, please contact our support team.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="/js/password-reset/reset-password-success.js"></script>
</body>
</html>